creator: DV Apps Store
descriptionHtml:
EPF Passbook: PF Balance, EPF Balance, UAN Appis providing various EPF services online for Indian employee. EPF Passbook helps you find your EPF Balance and Pension Details at anytime and anywhere.

EPF Passbook is an easy and smart way to check your EPF Balance without any hassle.

EPF Passbook: PF Balance, EPF Balance, UAN App offers you three modes to find out your EPF Balance.
1) Online
2) Call
3) SMS

Apart from EPF Balance EPF Passbook: PF Balance, EPF Balance, UAN App also offers various useful features to employees.In this app, employees can view all claim requests, EPF Passbook, verify/correct member details, Activate UAN, approve and submit the requests online through EPFO e-SEWA portal.You can also check your pension with one click.


Key Features:

• Check EPF Balance: Employees can check EPF Balance or PF Balance through UAN number and registered mobile number directly from EPFO e-SEWA portal. You can also download EPF Passbook.

• Check Pension Details: Check your Pension Payment Order (PPO) status provided on the Central Pension Accounting Office under the Ministry of Finance India website.Users can enter their 12 Digit PPO Number and Date of Birth to check the PPO status online.


• Check TRRN Status:Employers can check Temporary Return Reference Number (TRRN) Status through 13 Digit Number link & KYC Link update status.


• Activate UAN: You can easily activate your Universal Account Number (UAN) with ACTIVATE UAN feature.In case you forget your UAN, don't worry you can easily know your UAN through this app.


• Find Nearest EPFO office: You can easily find nearest EPFO office in your area.

• Helping Number: Now you can easily solve any queries related to EPF by just giving a call on a TOLL FREE NUMBER.

• EPFO e-SEWA Portal: This app developed in such way that it provides you an access to the EPFO e-SEWA portal even if you have low internet connection.




Disclaimer:
• This app is developed for users to get all useful and important links, information and help at one single place.
• This app is NOT an official app for EPF, neither this app is related to EPFO department.
• We are not associated or affiliated, directly or indirectly to government body.
